Detailed Description

cvmx_gmx::_bad_reg

GMX_BAD_REG = A collection of things that have gone very, very wrong

Notes: In XAUI mode, only the lsb (corresponding to port0) of INB_NXA, LOSTSTAT, OUT_OVR, are used.
